  "heading_path": "中文学术纯文风 Humanize Skill：生产化交付与红队报告 / 16. 常用命令",
  "intensity": "STRUCTURAL",
  "line_count": 72,
  "masked_text": "[[PROTECTED:F00001-P00600:a654f9242ad9]]\n短文扫描：\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P00601:8b9e65086998]]\n单独硬保护检查：\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P00602:c4a7ae569fef]]\n统一交付验证：\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P00603:f78dd5d522db]]\nsupplied-content DRAFT 表面来源验证：\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P00604:c45bf875be9c]]\n该命令即使表面来源门通过，也会在自然语言蕴含未获得可信逐分句 review 时返回\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P00605:8d0b66921bb6]] 与 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P00606:bd036b668dc6]]；不要把它手改成 PASS。\n\n带本地处理 proposal（仍返回 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P00607:bd036b668dc6]]）：\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P00608:d09c529a2ed9]]\n长文准备与收尾：\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P00609:9d783fefa7bb]]\n生成资格 public case 与本地 E2 采集：\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P00610:82e8f403b99f]]\n本地 runner 成功也只表示 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P00611:3b6958e442dd]]；没有外部隔离 receipt 时不要把命令输出改写为 E3。\n\n",
  "mode": "REWRITE",
